    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627570/extras/dc842ec34f597956bbc2bbcc77b6b57a.poster.avif?t=1757545827\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627570/extras/dc842ec34f597956bbc2bbcc77b6b57a.webm?t=1757545827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627570/extras/dc842ec34f597956bbc2bbcc77b6b57a.mp4?t=1757545827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《勇敢小骑士》讲述的是乔特和伙伴们的神奇冒险——他们原本是存在于故事书里的人物，突然意识到书页之外有个三维的世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627570/extras/4dfd826052267cadc68297554e2b7b8a.poster.avif?t=1757545827\" width=618 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627570/extras/4dfd826052267cadc68297554e2b7b8a.webm?t=1757545827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627570/extras/4dfd826052267cadc68297554e2b7b8a.mp4?t=1757545827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当邪恶的哼格兰普意识到自己是书中故事里的大反派，并在与正义一方的战争中永远没有获胜的可能时，他把英勇的乔特从书页中踢了出去，以期彻底改变故事的剧情。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627570/extras/e556329532b4489e45efeb717d3353b6.poster.avif?t=1757545827\" width=618 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627570/extras/e556329532b4489e45efeb717d3353b6.webm?t=1757545827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627570/extras/e556329532b4489e45efeb717d3353b6.mp4?t=1757545827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>乔特要从哼格兰普的黑暗势力手下拯救他的朋友、恢复书中故事的美好结局，为此他必须直面自己前所未见的挑战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627570/extras/bc57846c0263084333b6c28b3bc38e4b.poster.avif?t=1757545827\" width=618 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627570/extras/bc57846c0263084333b6c28b3bc38e4b.webm?t=1757545827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627570/extras/bc57846c0263084333b6c28b3bc38e4b.mp4?t=1757545827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在这段迷人的动作冒险游戏中，你将变成一本活生生的故事书中的人物，在2D与3D的世界间穿梭：破解谜题、与蜜獾搏斗、背着飞行背包飞翔，同时享受着各类迷你挑战为你带来的愉快与惊喜。",
